Wani ɗan shekara 13 ya ji rauni a lokacin da yake neman lobster a California
Wani ɗan shekara 13 ya ji rauni a lokacin da wani ɗan kifi ya kai masa hari a ranar Asabar yayin da yake ruwa don neman lobster a California a ranar farko ta kakar lobster, a cewar hukumomi.
An kai harin ne da misalin karfe 7 na safe a kusa da Beacon's Beach a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya bayyana wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa, yana tafiya ne da abokai na tsawon rabin sa'a a safiyar Asabar, sai ya ji wani yaro yana kuka don taimako, sai suka yi tuƙi tare da wasu mutane zuwa inda yaron yake don su taimake shi ya fita daga cikin ruwan.
Hammel ya ce da farko ya yi tunanin cewa yana farin ciki ne don ya kama wani kwari, amma sai ya lura cewa yana kuka 'An cije ni!
An yi mini ciwo!'
Yana da dukan clavicle tsage, ya lura Hammel a lõkacin da ya isa ga yaro.
"Saboda kowa yana fitowa daga cikin ruwa, sai na yi ihu, 'Akwai wani kifi a cikin ruwa!' " in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron ta hanyar iska zuwa Asibitin Yara na Rady a San Diego, inda aka shigar da shi cikin mawuyacin hali.
Ba a san irin kifin da ya kai harin ba.
A wani taron manema labarai, mai aikin agaji Larry Giles ya yi sharhi cewa a makonni da suka gabata an gano wani kifin a yankin, amma an yanke shawarar cewa wannan nau'in ba shi da haɗari.
Giles ya kara da cewa, wanda aka kashe yana da raunin da ya faru a saman kashinsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe tsawon sa'o'i 48 zuwa rairayin bakin teku daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas saboda bincike da kuma dalilai na tsaro.
Giles ya lura cewa akwai fiye da jinsunan shark 135 a yankin, amma yawancin su ba su da haɗari.
Shirye-shiryen Sainsbury's zuwa kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ya yanke shawarar yin gasa a Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da hanyoyin kayan kwalliya kamar manyan shagunan da ke cike da ƙwararrun ma'aikata.
Waɗannan manyan hanyoyin suna ɗaya ne kawai daga cikin babban saka hannun jari a kasuwar kayan kwalliya a Burtaniya, kasuwar da ke da fam biliyan 2.8 kuma tana ci gaba da ƙaruwa yayin da masana'antar kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke ci gaba da raguwa, kuma za a gwada su a shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar don faɗaɗa zuwa ƙarin shaguna a shekara mai zuwa idan gwajin ya yi nasara.
Zuba jari a kayayyakin kwalliya sakamakon son cin kasuwa ne na cinye sararin samaniya a kantunan su wanda a baya ya kasance don talabijin, microwaves da kayayyakin gida.
Sainsbury's ya ce zai ninka kayan kwalliyarsa na kyawawan abubuwa har zuwa kayayyaki daban-daban 3,000, gami da a karon farko alamomin kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
Tsarin L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees da ke akwai za su sami ƙarin sarari tare da yankunan alamun kama da waɗanda za a iya samu a shagunan kamar Boots.
Kamfanin kantin sayar da kayayyaki yana kuma cikin sake fasalin jerin kayan kwalliyar Boutique don yawancin samfuran yanzu sun dace da masu cin ganyayyaki, wani bangare da ake buƙata ta hanyar matasa masu amfani.
Shagon sayar da kayan ƙanshi, The Fragrance Shop, zai buɗe kantuna biyu na Sainsbury's, na farko a makon da ya gabata a Croydon, kudancin London, yayin da na biyu zai buɗe a Selly Oak, Birmingham, daga baya a wannan shekarar.
Sayayya ta Intanet da kuma sauya halin sayan abinci a ƙananan ƙananan kantuna a kowace rana ya sa manyan kantuna suna buƙatar neman wasu hanyoyi don shawo kan mutane su zo.
A cewar Mike Coupe, babban daraktan kamfanin Sainsbury's, shagunan za su zama kamar manyan kantuna a kokarin da kamfanin ke yi na yakar manyan kantunan Aldi da Lidl da ke sayar da kayayyakin abinci da sauran kayayyaki.
Sainsbury's ta gabatar da wuraren sayar da Argos a yawancin manyan kantunan ta, ban da kantunan Habitat tun lokacin da ta sayi duka sarƙoƙi biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda, ta ce, ya taimaka wajen sake fara sayar da kayan abinci da haɓaka ribar sayayya.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na babban kantin sayar da kayayyaki na sake buɗe sassan kayan kwalliya da kantin magani ya gaza.
Sainsbury's ya yi gwajin haɗin gwiwa tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma duk ya ƙare da sauri ba tare da sun yarda da yadda za a raba ribar da aka samu daga sarkar kantin magani a cikin manyan kantuna ba.
Wannan sabon dabarun ya zo ne bayan sayar da kasuwancinsa na kantuna 281 da Sainsbury's ya sayar wa Celesio, mai gidan sayar da kayayyakin magani na LloydsPharmacy, na fam miliyan 125 shekaru uku da suka gabata.
A cewar Sainsbury's, Lloyds zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin shirin na duniya, kamar yadda zai fadada kewayon samfuran samfuran fata na alatu, kamar La Roche-Posay ko Vichy, zuwa shaguna huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun canza yanayin da ke cikin hanyoyinmu na kayan kwalliya don inganta yanayin da muke fuskanta ga abokan cinikinmu.
Mun zuba jari a cikin ma'aikata da aka horar musamman waɗanda za su taimaka sosai wajen ba da shawara.
An tsara kewayon samfuranmu don dacewa da kowane buƙata; a gefe guda, kyakkyawan yanayi da wuri mai amfani sun sa yanzu mu zama ɗayan wuraren da aka fi so don kayan kwalliya kuma muna ƙalubalantar hanyar cin kasuwa ta gargajiya.
Peter Jones ya yi fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ta koma bayan yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Tauraron Dragons' Den Peter Jones ya yi "fushi" bayan mai gabatar da talabijin Holly Willoughby ta koma bayan yarjejeniyar GBP miliyan 11 tare da kasuwancin kasuwancin Jones don mai da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV.
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don yin kasuwancin haɗin gwiwar Truly na kayan gida da kayan haɗi.
An kwatanta kasuwancin waɗannan mutane biyu na kafofin watsa labarai da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, mai shekara 37, ta yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarta.
Holly Willoughby ya bar tauraron Dragons' Den Peter Jones cikin fushi ta hanyar janyewa a minti na ƙarshe daga kasuwancin haɗin gwiwar haɗin gwiwar don mai da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyoyinsa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV, waɗanda kuma za su kawo masa babban riba.
A cewar wasu majiyoyi, Jones ya yi "fushi" lokacin da tauraron talabijin mai launin ruwan kasa ya yarda, a lokacin wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali da aka gudanar a ranar Talata a hedkwatar mulkinsa a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyar mai gabatar da labarai, mai darajar GBP miliyan 1.5, na nufin ba za ta sami isasshen lokacin da za ta ba da haɗin gwiwar kayan gida da kayan haɗi na Truly ba.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand kuma yana da burin ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta a cikin GBP miliyan 11.
Lokacin da Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarsa daga Truly, Jones ya ɗauki jirgin sama mai zaman kansa zuwa ɗayan wuraren hutunsa na hutu a waje da Burtaniya.
A cewar wata majiya, "Truly ta kasance babban fifiko ga Holly.
An tsara ta ta zama makomar ta na dogon lokaci kuma inda za mu gan ta a cikin shekaru 20 zuwa 30 masu zuwa.
Ƙudurinsa na yin hakan ya sa dukan waɗanda suka sa hannu cikin wannan batun suka yi mamaki.
Ba wanda ya iya gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, mun kasance kusa da kaddamarwa...
A yanzu haka, akwai ɗakunan ajiya cike da kayayyaki a hedkwatar Marlow da za a sayar.
Masana sun ce, barin mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, daya daga cikin fitattun taurarin Burtaniya, zai iya sa kamfanin ya yi asarar miliyoyin daloli saboda yawan kudaden da aka zuba a kayayyakin, daga matashin kai da na'urar wanka zuwa tufafi da kayan gida, da kuma yiwuwar jinkiri wajen kaddamar da shi.
Ƙari ga haka, zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka na dogon lokaci.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar yara uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance da dangantaka ta kusa da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016, kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga matsayin shugaban a watan Maris na shekarar da ta gabata.
Dukansu ma'aurata suna hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakadan alama na M&S na gaba kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a jiya cewa "Ba za mu yi sharhi game da harkokin kasuwancinsa ba".
