Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya ci kwallo ta hudu da harbi mai nisa a gaban Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier ta Ingila a kan Chelsea da ci da ya ci a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge, London.
Sturridge ya karbi wani wasa daga Xherdan Shaqiri a mita 27 daga kofar Chelsea yayin da tawagarsa ta yi rashin nasara da ci 1-0.
Ya kwantar da kwallon zuwa hagu kafin ya saki wani bugun da ya kai ga sanda ta biyu.
Harbin ya ratsa yankin da babban tsawo yayin da yake motsawa zuwa ga dama na ƙofar.
A ƙarshe sai ƙwallon ya fara sauka a kan Kepa Arrizabalaga a tsalle don ƙoƙarin dakatar da shi kuma ya ƙare a ƙasan raga.
"Ina kokarin zuwa wannan matsayi ne kawai domin in iya harba, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaqiri suna buga shi gaba da gaba, don haka na yi kokarin samar da lokaci mai yawa", in ji Sturridge a LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kanté yana zuwa, na yi wasa, ban yi tunani sosai ba, na mai da hankali ga yin wasa".
Chelsea ta ci 1-0 a hutun bayan da ta ci kwallo a minti na 25 ta hanyar dan wasan ta na Belgium Eden Hazard.
A wasan, dan wasan Blue ya koma da baya a kan Mateo Kovacic kafin ya fara daga kusan tsakiyar filin kuma ya yi tsalle zuwa filin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi saurin hadawa daga tsakiyar filin wasa.
Bayan haka, ya yi babban motsawa a cikin zurfin, wanda ya bar Hazard a cikin yankin tare da ball a sarrafa.
Hazard ya zarce kariya don gamawa a kan ƙwallon na biyu tare da bugun da ya yi da ƙafar hagu inda mai tsaron gidan Liverpool Alisson Becker bai iya isa ba.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Laraba da ke tafe da karfe 3 na yamma a Stadio San Paolo da ke birnin Naples na Italiya.
