Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli jawabin Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafinsa a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a ranar Alhamis, wanda aka watsa a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da tashoshin watsa shirye-shirye na dakatar da shirye-shiryen ranar Juma'a saboda juyin juya halin minti na ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da binciken tuhuma na mako guda.
Ford ta bayyana wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taba ta cikin maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinta a wani bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya yi, ya ce ya tabbata cewa wannan bai taɓa faruwa ba.
A cewar Nielsen, akwai yiwuwar sama da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan shaidar a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin yana da matsakaicin masu sauraro na tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun adadin masu sauraro nan take a wasu tashoshin da suka watsa wannan shaidar, kamar su PBS, C-SPAN ko Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yakan sami matsala wajen ƙididdige mutanen da suke kallon shi daga ofishinsa.
Idan aka kwatanta da wannan, wannan taron yana kama da wasan wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na wasan playoffs ko bikin Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wadda shugabannin ra'ayoyin jama'a suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ita ce tashar da ta fi yawan masu sauraro, inda ta samu kimanin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin rana daya, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 da NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 da kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52 bisa ga bayanan Nielsen.
Sha'awa tana da yawa bayan shaidar.
Flake shine babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin Jam'iyyar ta moderate ya fitar da sanarwa cewa za su kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, Flake ya kama ta kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga suka kama shi yayin da yake kokarin hawa kan lif don zuwa taron kwamitin shari'a.
Flake ya kasance na mintuna da yawa tare da idonsa a yayin da aka sake shi ta hanyar talabijin ta CNN.
"Ga ni nan, a gabanka", in ji wata mace.
Kana ganin yana gaya wa kasar gaskiya?
An ce masa, 'kai kana da iko, amma akwai mata da yawa da ba su da iko!'
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da sanarwa kuma kafin a rufe kofofin lif, ya ce zai kara da cewa a gaban kwamitin.
Cikin sa'o'i kadan, duk tashoshin watsa shirye-shiryen talabijin da na wayoyin sadarwa sun fara watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a lokacin da kwamitin shari'a zai yi zabe kan ko zai ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh a gaban majalisar dattawa don jefa shi a kuri'a.
Flake ya ce, a maimakon haka, zai yi hakan ne kawai idan ya fahimci cewa FBI za ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, wanda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya shawo kan wannan batu ne ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na jam'iyyar Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Zaɓin da Flake ya zaɓa yana da tasiri, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami isassun kuri'u don tallafawa Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude wani bincike na FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
Firayim Minista May ta zargi masu sukar ta da yin siyasa kan batun Brexit
Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirin ta na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai da 'wasa siyasa' da makomar Burtaniya da kuma raina bukatun kasa a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
