A wata hira da ta yi da May a shafin jaridar, tsohon ministan harkokin wajen May Boris Johnson ya kara kai hari kan shirin da ake kira Chequers na Brexit, inda ya ce shawarar da ake yi na Birtaniya da EU su tara haraji a kan juna "sabo ne".
Wayde Sims harin bindiga: 'Yan sanda sun kama wanda ake zargi da aikata laifin Dyteon Simpson saboda mutuwar dan wasan kungiyar LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani wanda ake zargi da harbin Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando mai shekara 20 da ke taka leda a kungiyar LSU.
An kama mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an kai shi kurkuku bisa laifin kisan kai na biyu, in ji sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
