Bayan an yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, sai ya yarda cewa ya kashe Wayde da bindiga, a cewar 'yan sanda.
An kafa belin ta a kan dala 350,000, kamar yadda lauyan ta ruwaito.
Ofishin likitan shari'ar yankin East Baton Rouge ya fitar da rahoto na farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce dalilin mutuwar ta kasance wani harbi da aka yi masa a kai da ya kai ga wuyansa.
Sashen na gode wa rundunar 'yan sanda da ke Louisiana, da ma'aikatar bincike na 'yan sanda, da jami'ar 'yan sanda ta Kudu da kuma' yan ƙasa da ke yankin don taimakon da suka bayar a binciken da ya kai ga kama wannan mutumin.
Daraktan wasanni na LSU Joe Alleva ya nuna godiyarsa ga jami'an tsaro na yankin saboda 'hankulansu' da kuma neman adalci.
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Ya kasance mai tsayi 1.98 cm, yana wasa da mai tsalle-tsalle kuma ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, shi ma dan wasan kwando ne a kungiyar LSU.
Ya kai kimanin maki 5.6 da kuma rebounds 2.6 a farkon kakar wasan da ta gabata.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, kocin kwando na kungiyar LSU Will Wade ya ce kungiyar ta "ruɓe" kuma mutuwar Wayde "ta yi matukar rauni".
"Abin da ke sa ka wahala a kowane lokaci", in ji Wade.
