Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin mutunci da kuma fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Zaɓen da aka yi wa Kavanaugh ya nuna rashin amincewa da makircin da jam'iyyar Democrat ke yi", in ji Trump a wani taron zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin hankali da kuma fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a duk lokacin da aka nada shi.
Kavanaugh ya shaida wa majalisa a ranar Alhamis, yana musanta zargi da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi masa na cin zarafinta shekaru da yawa da suka gabata, lokacin da suke matasa.
Ford ya kuma yi shaida a gaban kotu dangane da zargin da ake masa.
