Shugaban Mexico AMLO ya yi alkawarin ba zai yi amfani da dakarun soja ba wajen yaki da fararen hula
Shugaban kasar Mexico da aka zaba, Andres Manuel López Obrador, ya yi alkawarin ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja kan fararen hula ba, a lokacin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kisan gilla da aka yi wa dalibai.
A ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco, Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba za a sake amfani da dakarun soji ba don murkushe mutanen Mexico.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojojin sun bude wuta a lokacin zanga-zangar lumana kuma sun kashe mutane 300 a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗaliban ɗalibai na hagu ke kafa tushe a duk faɗin Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador, wanda ya yi alkawarin tallafa wa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga ɗalibai da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in jama'a kyauta,
ya bayyana cewa rashin aikin yi da rashin damar ilimi suna janyo matasa zuwa ƙungiyoyin masu laifi.
Dole ne Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
"Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfi a fannin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a fannin", in ji Kai-Fu Lee, wani mai zuba jari da kuma kwararre a fannin kere kere wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan jawabin ya zo ne bayan wasu mambobin gwamnatin Amurka sun sanar da matakan da suka dauka kan batun AI, duk da cewa kasar ba ta da wata dabara ta musamman kan AI.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta na shekara ta bara, inda take da burin zama kasa ta farko a duniya wajen kirkirar AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Abu ne mai kyau a fara ninka kasafin kudin da ake kashewa wajen binciken AI, saboda sauran kasashen duniya sun yi kasa da Amurka kuma muna son zama jagororin ci gaban AI na gaba", in ji Lee.
"Haɗa kuɗin zai iya ninka damar da Amurka za ta samu na babbar sabuwar fasahar kere kere", in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, marubucin littafin nan mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ta wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne babban daraktan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin.
A cikin 1980 ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya wuce ɗan wasan Amurka na Othello tare da mafi kyawun matsayi kuma, daga baya, ya yi aiki a matsayin mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma a matsayin shugaban reshen China na Google.
Lee ya ba da kyakkyawan ra'ayi game da gasa ta fasaha ta Gwamnatin Amurka, kamar DARPA's Robotics Challenge, kuma ya yi mamakin lokacin da za a yi na gaba don gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
"Yawancin lokaci, masu bincike na Amurka suna bukatar su yi aiki tukuru domin samun tallafin gwamnati", in ji Lee.
Lee ya ce, "Ba kasar Sin ce ke jan ragamar shugabannin ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne".
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan jami'o'i don yin aiki a fagen AI.
Lee ya yi sharhi cewa aikin Amurka a fagen AI na iya samun ci gaba tare da sauye-sauye a manufofin shige da fice.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a samar da katin zama na dindindin ga daliban PhD a IA", in ji shi.
A watan Yulin 2017, Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin bunkasa fasahar kere kere ta zamani.
"Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da tallafi ga jami'an kimiyya kamar yadda Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa da sauran hukumomin gwamnati a Amurka ke ba da tallafi ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya ya yi kasa da na kasar Sin", in ji Lee.
A farkon shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kirkiro Cibiyar Haɗin Kai na Artificial Intelligence, wanda aka tsara don masu haɗin gwiwar masana'antu da cibiyoyin ilimi su shiga, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓin Artificial Intelligence.
Haka kuma a wannan watan DARPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri da ake kira AI Next.
Game da Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Halitta, a yanzu haka tana kashe sama da dala miliyan 100 a shekara don bincike kan AI.
A halin yanzu, an shafe watanni ba a aiwatar da wani mataki dangane da dokar Amurka da ke nufin kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa kan Ilimin Artificial Intelligence.
'Yan Macedonia sun gudanar da kuri'ar raba gardama kan ko za su canja sunan kasar
A ranar Lahadin da ta gabata, mutanen Macedonia sun gudanar da kuri'ar raba gardama kan sauya sunan zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia, matakin da zai warware takaddama da ta dade da shekaru da dama da Girka, wadda ta toshe bukatar Macedonia ta shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wacce ke da lardin da ake kira Macedonia, ta yi ikirarin cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa na da'awar mallakar yankin ta kuma ta hana ta shiga NATO da EU.
A watan Yuni, gwamnatocin biyu sun cimma yarjejeniya kan sabon sunan da aka gabatar, amma masu adawa da kishin kasa sun yi jayayya cewa canjin zai lalata asalin kabilanci na yawan mutanen Slavic na Macedonia.
Shugaban kasar Gyorge Ivanov ya bayyana cewa ba zai shiga zaben ba, kuma yakin neman zabe na nuna shakku kan ko za a kai matakin kasafin kashi 50 na masu halartar zaben domin zaben ya zama mai inganci.
Tambayar da aka nuna a takardar kuri'ar ita ce: Shin kuna goyon bayan shiga NATO da EU, tare da yarda da yarjejeniyar da aka yi da Girka?.
Magoya bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi jayayya cewa farashin da ya cancanci biya ne don samun Macedonia, daya daga cikin kasashen da suka samo asali daga rushewar Yugoslavia, zuwa kungiyoyi kamar EU da NATO.
"Na zo ne don na kada kuri'a a yau a kan makomar kasar, domin matasa na Macedonia su sami 'yanci su zauna a cikin Tarayyar Turai, domin hakan na nufin cewa dukkanmu za mu sami kwanciyar hankali", in ji Olivera Georgijevska, 'yar shekara 79, a Skopje.
Ko da yake ba shi da tilastawa bisa doka, 'yan majalisa da dama sun bayyana cewa za su amince da sakamakon zaben don yin shi mai yanke hukunci.
Don canza sunan, ana buƙatar rinjaye na kashi biyu bisa uku a cikin Majalisa.
Hukumar zabe ta jihar ta ruwaito cewa babu wani rashin daidaito da ya faru a karfe 1 na yamma.
Koyaya, halartar ta kasance kashi 16 kawai, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34% da aka yi a zaɓen majalisa na ƙarshe, wanda aka gudanar a 2016, inda kashi 66% na waɗanda suka yi rajista suka jefa ƙuri'a.
"Na zo ne domin in zabe 'ya'yana, inda muke a Turai", in ji Gjose Tanevski, mai shekara 62, a babban birnin kasar Skopje.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia, Zoran Zaev, matarsa Zorica da ɗansa Dushko sun kada kuri'ar raba gardama da aka gudanar a Macedonia kan sauya sunan ƙasar, wanda zai buɗe hanyar shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO a Strumica, Macedonia, a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018.
A gaban majalisar dokokin Skopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov, mai shekara 54, yana shirya karamin mataki kuma yana ajiye kujeru a gaban alfarwa da mutane da ke son kauracewa zaben suka kafa.
"Muna goyon bayan NATO da EU, amma muna son shiga da kai, ba ta ƙofar baya ba", in ji Kavadarkov.
Kasarmu matalauta ce, amma muna da mutunci.
Idan ba sa son su yarda da mu a matsayin Macedonia, za mu iya zuwa wasu ƙasashe, kamar China da Rasha, mu shiga cikin haɗin kan Yuro-Asiya.
Firayim Minista Zaev ya ce shiga NATO zai zo tare da zuba jari fiye da yadda ake bukata a Macedonia, wanda ke da rashin aikin yi sama da 20%.
"Ina ganin cewa mafiya yawa za su amince da shi, domin sama da kashi 80 cikin 100 na 'yan kasar na goyon bayan Tarayyar Turai da NATO", in ji Zaev kafin ya ajiye takardar.
Zaev ya bayyana cewa "Ee" zai zama "tabbatar da makomarmu".
A wani binciken da Cibiyar Bincike ta Siyasa ta Macedonia ta fitar a ranar Litinin, tsakanin kashi 30 zuwa 43 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a za su shiga cikin kuri'ar, wanda ya kai kasa da matakin da ake bukata na shiga.
A cewar wani binciken da tashar Telma TV ta kasar Macedonia ta gudanar, kashi 57% na masu jefa kuri'a na shirin kada kuri'arsu a ranar Lahadi.
Daga cikin su, kashi 70 cikin 100 sun ce za su yi zabe da "YES".
Domin kuri'ar raba gardama ta zama mai inganci, dole ne a samu kashi 50 cikin 100 da kuri'a daya.
Rashin nasara a zaben raba gardama zai zama na farko da ya kai ga siyasa ta gwamnatin da ke goyon bayan Yammacin Turai tun lokacin da ta fara mulki a watan Mayu na shekarar da ta gabata.
