Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: wasu Ayr da ba a doke su ba sun jagoranci
Gwaji biyu na ƙarshe sun gurɓata sakamakon ƙarshe, amma babu shakka Ayr sun cancanci nasara a wannan wasa mai cike da tashin hankali na ranar Tennent's Premiership.
Ayr, wanda shine kadai tawagar da ba a doke ta ba daga cikin goma, suna kan gaba a teburin.
A ƙarshe, ƙungiyar gida ta yi nasara ta hanyar tsaronta da kuma gaskiyar cewa sun san yadda za su yi amfani da dama mafi kyau, kuma kocin Peter Murchie yana da dalilai na gamsuwa.
"Kwallon da muka buga ya gwada mu kuma har yanzu ba a doke mu ba, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki", in ji shi.
Robyn Christie daga Melrose ta ce: "Muna taya 'yan Ayr murna, sun yi amfani da damar da suka samu fiye da yadda muka yi amfani da ita".
Gwadawar Grant Anderson a minti na 14, wanda Frazier Climo ya canza, ya sa Ayr gaba, amma katin rawaya ga ɗan wasan Scotland Rory Hughes, wanda Warriors suka ba da shi don wasan, ya ba Melrose damar cin gajiyar lambar yabo kuma Jason Baggot ya rubuta gwajin da ba a canza shi ba.
Climo ya karawa Ayr nasara da wata takarda kuma a tsakiyar wasan ya ci kwallo kuma ya juya kwallo don sanya maki 17-5 a kan Ayr a hutu.
Amma Melrose sun fara wasan na biyu da kyau kuma gwajin Patrick Anderson, wanda Baggot ya canza, ya rage bambancin zuwa maki biyar.
Bayan haka, wasan ya tsaya na dogon lokaci saboda mummunan rauni da Ruaridh Knott ya sha, wanda ya yi ritaya a kan gado, kuma a sake dawowa Ayr sun sake fadada nesa tare da gwajin Stafford McDowall wanda Climo ya canza.
