Tauraruwar wasan kwaikwayo na Still Game kamar tana shirin fara sabon aiki a masana'antar abinci
Ford Kieran, tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Still Game, ya bayyana a matsayin wanda zai koma harkar karbar baki, bayan da aka gano cewa an nada shi darakta na kamfanin cin abinci mai lasisi.
