Masu zanen kaya Valentino da Thom Browne sun gabatar da wasu kyawawan kyawawan tufafi masu girman gaske daga tarin su na SS19 a kan titin, wanda ya haskaka salon da aka ayyana a Makon Fashion na Paris.
A wannan bazarar Instagram ta sha fama da wasu abubuwa marasa amfani, kuma waɗannan masu zanen kaya sun kawo abubuwan ban mamaki a kan titi.
