LeBron zai fara wasa da Lakers a San Diego ranar Lahadi
Dakatarwar ta kusan karewa ga magoya bayan da suke son ganin LeBron James ya buga wasan farko da Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma har yanzu ana bukatar a ƙayyade lokacin da za a yi wasa.
"Za su fi daya da kasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mike Trudell, dan jaridar Lakers, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasan ne na 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan atisayen farko na wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasan Lakers na wasanni shida.
"Ba na bukatar wasannin bazara a wannan lokaci na aikina don in kasance a shirye", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani yunkuri na yakin neman zabe a wannan daren a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar zuwa wurare masu kyau, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran kuri'ar tabbatar da dan takararsa na cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun koli, Trump na son samun goyon baya a zaben rabin-zamanin da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar hatsarin rasa iko a majalisa lokacin da aka kada kuri'u a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne da karfe 7 na yamma a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za a iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube a kan hanyar da aka ambata a ƙasa.
Trump zai yi jawabi a shari'ar da aka fara a wannan makon tare da dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya fuskanci tashin hankali saboda zargin cin zarafin da ake masa, yayin da aka dage zaben tabbatar da kujerar dattijai har mako guda, kuma FBI na binciken lamarin.
Amma babban dalilin wannan zanga-zangar shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke takara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba su samu ci gaba.
Saboda haka, tarurrukan yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, suna da nufin karfafa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa na da muhimmanci a ajandar shugaban kasa, kuma zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama, yayin da muke fuskantar lokacin kamfen mai cike da jama'a", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa, a cewar Reuters.
Taron da za a yi yau da dare a Wesbanco Arena, Wheeling, zai iya tara masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, kamar yadda West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, wanda ke samun sakamako mara kyau a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa zai zo ya ba shi ci gaba a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: tawagar Amurka ta nuna burinta na ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a wasannin da za a buga a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi zaman rashin daidaito sau uku, wasannin hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma sun kasance abin da gasar Ryder Cup ke bukata.
Dandalin motsa jiki na motsa jiki wani ra'ayi ne na wasanni wanda 'yan wasa suka yi imani da shi, musamman a irin wannan gasar.
To, a wace hanya ce muke samun ci gaba mai kyau?
"Sun yi nasara da maki shida kuma yanzu ya kai hudu, don haka ina ganin muna kan karamin matakin da ya dace", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake barin wasan a karshen ranar.
A bayyane yake, Turai tana da nasara, maki huɗu a gaba, tare da ƙarin goma sha biyu a cikin wasa.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa iska tana busawa a cikin ni'imarsu kuma suna da dalilai da yawa don yin farin ciki, galibi saboda yanayin yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma dukansu suna da maki uku daga huɗu.
Spieth ya yi kisa tun daga tee-up zuwa green kuma yana kafa misali.
Kiran murna ya karu yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye kuma ya buga wani muhimmin wasa don daidaita wasan na huɗu, lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu a ƙasa bayan ramuka biyu.
Ya yi murnar buga kwallo da ya sa suka ci wasan a rami na 15 da irin wannan ihu, irin wanda ya nuna cewa yana ganin tawagar Amurka har yanzu ba ta fita daga gasar ba.
"Ya kamata ka yi iyakar ƙoƙarinka ka kuma damu da ƙungiyarka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne duk abin da waɗannan 'yan wasan suka rage a yanzu.
Rami 18 don yin burbushin.
'Yan wasa guda da suka fi Spieth da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wanda ba a iya shakkarsa ba a gasar Ryder.
Ma'aurata na Turai masu ban mamaki amma masu ban sha'awa suna sa hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba su yi kuskure ba.
Moliwood su ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, kuma sun kuma guje wa bogeys a ranar Asabar da yamma da kuma Jumma'a da yamma, da kuma tara na ƙarshe a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Saboda wannan sakamakon da kuma yadda yake daukan nauyinsa daga cikin jama'a, ya tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su doke ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari shahara wajen rufe wata nasara ta Turai yayin da rana ta sauka a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau a yi duka biyu a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Amma, magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ba ta da wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin gamawa da Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Alex Noren.
Bogey da biyu a cikin ramuka tara na farko sun jefa Mutanen Espanya da Swede cikin rami wanda ba su da wani zaɓi na fita.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga cikin ramin.
Kwallan kwallo da kuma na hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai a kallon su saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin na'urori, da shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun ke iya canzawa ba zato ba tsammani.
Ya zuwa yanzu, Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar kuma za ta fuskanci ranar karshe da babbar nasara, amma wannan zaman na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da kwarin gwiwar yin gwagwarmaya da wasu, musamman Amurka, suka yi tambaya.
Turai ta kai wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup da ci 10-6
Turai za ta fuskanci ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da saukin kai bayan kammala wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu a ranar Asabar da nasara 10-6 a kan Amurka.
The inspirational duo kafa ta Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sanya wani babban kokarin cimma biyu wins da Tiger Woods a cikin matsaloli da kuma barin rikodin, har zuwa yanzu, a hudu maki a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai, wadda Thomas Bjorn ya jagoranci, wadda ke neman riƙe kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye wani rukunin 'yan wasan Amurka da suka yi rashin nasara a wasan kwallon kafa na safe kuma suka ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi tsayayya da wasan hudu kuma ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage bambance-bambance ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk ta bukaci maki takwas a wasanni 12 da suka yi a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci nasara.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya fara cin kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka sani da suna Molliwood bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune kawai ma'aurata na biyu da suka sami maki huɗu a wasanninsu huɗu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa, sun yi fice sosai don doke Woods da dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu 'yan wasa masu ban mamaki, amma ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a wasan kwallon kafa da hudu, da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda bai shiga wasan kwallon kafa na safe ba, ya sake haɗuwa da Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu kuma ya fadi 2 zuwa 1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, waɗanda suka kasance na farko da na uku a duniya, bi da bi.
Amma, Turai ba ta da komai a gabanta a rana mai iska mai kyau a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali a ranar Asabar ga Amurkawa ta hanyar samun maki biyu.
Sun yi nasara da ƙuduri 2-1 a kan ɗan ƙasar Sifen Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan kwallon kafa kuma daga baya suka sake cin Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a wasan hudu, bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta samu tazarar maki hudu a wasannin mutum, duk da cewa tawagar Furyk, mai kare taken, kawai tana bukatar ta daidaita don kiyaye shi.
Amma bayan ya kasance na biyu a rana biyu, kamar dai wani hari a ranar Lahadi yana gab da shi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makaman ta ba har sai an amince da ita
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da kakabawa kasar na kara tsananta masa kan Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayi kasar ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron kungiyar shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakan kyakkyawar niyya" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, da kuma dakatar da cibiyar gwajin nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ba za ta kara samar da makaman nukiliya da fasaha ba.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani da ya yi daidai da na Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a sami amincewa da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a wannan yanayin, ba za mu fara kawar da makamai ba.
Duk da yake Ri ya karɓi sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington ga tsarin kawar da makaman nukiliya ta hanyar matakai wanda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da take ɗaukar matakai a hankali, maganganunsa sun yi kama da ma'ana saboda bai ƙi ƙin kawar da makaman nukiliya ta gefe ɗaya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da sanarwar da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "rashin makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce kafin hakan, dole ne Pyongyang ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi tsayayya da kiran sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace cewa dole ne a fara kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko kuma ta kara matsin lamba tare da takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, ban da adawa da "yanke dokar kare yaki", "in ji Ri.
"Hankalin da muke da shi cewa takunkumi zai sa mu durƙusa a kan gwiwoyinmu, ruɗu ne daga mutanen da ba su san kome ba game da mu.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da kakabawa kasar nan na kara sa mu cikin halin rashin amincewa da ita.
Ri bai yi magana game da shirin gudanar da taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya yi nuni da tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kuma kara da cewa: Idan bangaren da ke cikin batun hana makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, da ba za a sami wannan yanayin ba .
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bambam da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya bayyana a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa kai hari ga Amurka tare da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "Mr. Evil" a matsayin "Rocket Man" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya", ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa na ɗaukar matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da za a yi wannan kuma ba zai yi matsala ba ko shekaru biyu ne, ko uku ko watanni biyar.
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakin da ta dauka.
Sai dai kuma sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya bayyana a ranar Alhamis a majalisar tsaro ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin majalisar tsaro ba tare da wani abin da ya rage ba har sai mun tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya gaba daya".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da takunkumin da aka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa tun a shekarar 2006 a wani mataki na yanke kudaden da ake baiwa Pyongyang don harin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya sanar da cewa zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin "bukatun da suka dace da 'yan bindiga".
A wani taro da Moon ya yi a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe cibiyar makamai masu linzami da kuma cibiyar nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakai masu dacewa".
Ya ce Kim ya sanar da shi cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sune matakan tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore, ban da ayyuka don daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna koyar da darasi game da yadda ake hutawa
A wannan shekarar, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya ba dalibansa damar samun karin barci a wani yunkuri na yaki da al'adar karatun dare da rana da ke kara yaduwa, wanda ke cike da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masani ya lura cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, Farfesa a Harkokin Magungunan Barci a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da na Mata, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko na irin wannan a Amurka.
Ya yi wannan darasi ne bayan ya yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen wannan jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina, ta ce, "Me ya sa ake gaya mini haka a yanzu, a shekarata ta karshe?"
Ya ce babu wanda ya taba gaya masa muhimmancin barci, abin da ya ba ni mamaki, in ji shi a jaridar The Telegraph.
A wannan darasi, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a wannan shekara, an bayyana wa ɗalibai muhimman abubuwa game da yadda halayen bacci masu kyau ke inganta aikin ilimi da wasanni, ban da jin daɗin rayuwa.
Paul Barreira, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halin dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma babban daraktan ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya bayyana cewa jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan da ta samu labarin cewa wasu dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci sosai a cikin mako.
Darasin, na tsawon awa daya, ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani bangare akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai za su danna kofi, labule, takalma, da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda wasan motsa jiki ke shafar rashin barci, da kuma muhimmancin kiyaye al'ada ta barci.
Wani sashe kuma ya sanar da masu halarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara musu hadarin ciwon zuciya, ciwon jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar da ke dauke da gumaka masu ma'ana tana ƙarfafa mahalarta su yi tunanin hanyarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa halin ɗalibai ba zai canza nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin su san hakan, kamar yadda mutum yake da hakkin ya san illar shan sigari", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce al'adun alfahari da kasancewa a farke har dare har yanzu suna nan, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma karuwar matsin lamba da ake yiwa dalibai na sa rashin bacci ya zama babbar matsala.
Ya ce, tabbatar da samun isasshen bacci ya kamata ya zama wani abu da dalibai ke amfani da shi wajen yaki da damuwa da gajiya da kuma damuwa, har ma don guje wa samun nauyi, domin rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin rashin lafiya kuma yana sa dalibai su kasance cikin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan California mai shekara 19 da ke nazarin ilimin kimiyyar lissafi da ilimin kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekara ta ƙarshe a shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Raymond ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa ido kuma ya sa ya inganta shi a duk faɗin harabar.
Mataki na gaba, kamar yadda yake fata, shi ne a nemi daliban digiri na biyu su yi irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga cikin wannan cibiyar.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci ɗalibai su yi la'akari da sanya ƙararrawa a lokacin da suke barci da lokacin da suke farkawa, kuma su san da illa mai illa na Blue Light da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da fitilun LED, wanda zai iya lalata jituwa na circadian da kuma haifar da matsalolin bacci.
