Almanac: wanda ya kirkiro Geiger counter
Kuma yanzu shafi na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce - ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba, Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, wata dabara da ta haifar da na'urar da muke kira computator Geiger.
Geiger counter, wanda ya kasance ginshiƙi na kimiyya tun daga lokacin, ya zama babban al'adun al'adu, kamar fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka buga, wasu 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na rashin nasara:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Gidan lissafin Geiger ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo, kamar su Uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da atoms ke yi wa ma'adanai".
Evans: "Lalle ne yana da zafi yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki bayan ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya yi da sunansa yana nan.
Wani sabon maganin rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu ganin ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa
Wani sabon maganin rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinka yadda za ta iya ganewa da kuma kawar da kwayoyin cutar kansa
Rigakafin yana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum gane kwayoyin cutar a matsayin wani bangare na magani
Wannan hanya ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya da kuma canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Za ka iya ganin furotin da ke da amfani a yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan ka sake saka su a cikin kwayar.
Wani rigakafin gwaji yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan ciwon daji daban-daban.
Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafin, wadda take koya wa jikinta yadda zai gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon daji na ƙwanƙwasawa ya ɓace, wanda ta sha wahala fiye da watanni 18.
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga mai haƙuri, canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don "ganin" furotin da ke cikin nau'ikan ciwon daji da yawa (HER2) kuma, daga baya, sake yin allurar su.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon da muka samu ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafin da ke da kyau".
Furotin HER2  yana taimakawa ci gaban nau'ikan ciwon daji, ciki har da na nono, na ovarian, na huhu da na colorectal, kamar yadda Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana.
Irin wannan hanya ta cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga marasa lafiya da kuma koya wa waɗannan ƙwayoyin yadda za a bi da ƙwayoyin ciwon daji ya yi aiki a maganin wani nau'in cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya shiga cikin wata muhawara ta pro-Trump tare da hat na MAGA bayan wasan kwaikwayon sa a SNL.
Ba ta ƙare da kyau ba
An yi wa Kanye West fyade a gidan rediyon Saturday Night Live bayan wani mummunan wasan kwaikwayon da ya yi na taya Shugaba Donald Trump murnar tsayawa takarar shugabancin Amurka a 2020.
Bayan waƙar ta uku ta daren, mai taken Ghost Town, inda ta saka hular Make America Great Again, ta fara sukar 'yan Democrat da kuma sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Duk lokacin da nake magana da fararen fata, sai su ce, 'Ta yaya za ka so Trump idan shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?
To, idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
Shirin SNL ya fara ne da wani wasan kwaikwayo na Matt Damon, inda tauraron Hollywood ya yi wa shaidar Brett Kavanaugh ba'a a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Kodayake ba a watsa shi ba, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock ya ɗora rikodin rashin amincewar West a kan kafofin watsa labarun.
Ba a bayyana ba ko Rock yana nufin ya yi wa West ba'a tare da buga shi.
Koyaya, West ya koka ga jama'a cewa ba a kula da shi da kyau a bayan fage ba saboda hat ɗin da yake sakawa.
"An yi min barazana a bayan fage.
An gaya mini kada in fita da wannan hat.
An yi mini barazana.
Sai suka ce ni na kasa", in ji shi, a cewar jaridar Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba, "Kuna son ganin matsayi na ƙasa?" yayin da yake cewa zai sa mayafin Superman saboda ba za su iya gaya masa abin da zai yi ba. "Shin kuna son duniya ta ci gaba?
Ka yi kokarin kimantawa".
Maganganunsa sun haifar da zargi daga jama'a a kalla sau biyu kuma membobin ƙungiyar shirin sun zama kamar sun kunyata, a cewar Variety, wanda akwai wani ɗan rahoto wanda ya bayyana wa littafin: "Duk binciken ya zama shiru".
West ya kasance a matsayin maye gurbin Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon sa, Mac Miller ya mutu kwanakin baya.
West ya ba da mamaki ga yawancin masu sauraro tare da yin waƙar I Love it, wanda aka yi wa Perrier.
