HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS.
Akwai sama da mutane 820,000 da cutar ta shafa a kasar, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kawai an ba da rahoton sabbin mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na kamuwa da jima'i ne, ba kamar yadda ya kasance ba.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta hanyar wannan cuta ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, shekara shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da mutum 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga LGBT ya zama ruwan dare.
Bisa ga ra'ayin mazan jiya na ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin luwadi za su yi aure da mace.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake yadawa suna faruwa ne saboda rashin yin jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya leƙa bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican kuma ta yi watsi da "karya mai haɗari" da kuma "ka'idodin maƙarƙashiya".
