Bayanin ya fito ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku sun kalubalanci Kavanaugh.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen abubuwan da aka buga yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma yana bayyana bayanin wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Capitol ya ba da rahoton.
