A cewar jam'iyyar, shugabannin kamfanoni suna son su ba da kuɗin da aka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha na wucin gadi (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su karin ranar hutu.
Ma'aikata za su ji daɗin hutun mako na kwana uku, amma za su sami albashi ɗaya.
A cewar majiyoyin, ra'ayin zai dace da ajandar tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin karkatar da kasar ga masu aiki.
Canjin zuwa mako guda na aiki na kwana hudu yana da goyon bayan ƙungiyar Trades Union Congress a matsayin hanya don ma'aikata su sami fa'ida daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani masani a jam'iyyar Labor ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa, ana sa ran za a sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
