Menene bikin Global Citizen? Shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na kiɗa da ake yi a kowace shekara, wanda ke nuna wasu taurari masu ban sha'awa, waɗanda suke da manufa mai ban sha'awa: su kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane sun taru a yankin Great Lawn na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da burin duniya na kawar da matsanancin talauci a duniya kafin 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani bangare ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke taimakawa wajen yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan wani yana son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halarta dole ne su yi wasu ayyuka ko "ayyuka", kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko wani abu don wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Waɗanne nasarori ne Global Citizen ta samu yanzu da take da shekaru 12 kafin ta kai ga burinta?
Wannan ra'ayin na baiwa mutane kyauta ta hanyar yin wasa kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta shawo kan mutane su nemi kira zuwa aiki ko kuma wani abu ne da muke kira "clictivism" (wanda kuke ganin ya bambanta da sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga masu goyon bayanta, wanda ya taimaka wajen cimma manufofi da dama.
Ya ce wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen karfafawa shugabannin duniya gwiwa wajen sanar da kudade da manufofi masu kama da na dala biliyan 37, wanda zai shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.250 kafin shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da aka samu daga hannun jarin ta, wanda a kalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko aka tara.
Kungiyar ta kimanta cewa a halin yanzu asusun ajiyar kuɗi sun yi tasiri kai tsaye ga kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition Foundation, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu yin fim da ke zaune a Burtaniya, wanda ya yi alkawarin "taimaka wa yara su girma yadda ya kamata" kuma ya yi alkawarin aikawa da Rwanda dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen magance rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Ta hanyar goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da kuma 'yan Global Citizens kamar ku, za mu iya mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihin tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ga taron jama'a a lokacin wani wasan kwaikwayo na kai tsaye a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma bayyana cewa bayan fiye da ayyuka 5,000 da ke kira ga Burtaniya don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na uwaye da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade don wani shiri, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da maganganun abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wani shafi na P+F a shafinsa na yanar gizo wanda ya tambaya "me ya sa kuke ganin za mu iya kawar da talauci mai tsanani?"
Global Citizen ta amsa, "Za mu yi tafiya mai tsawo da wuya, wani lokacin za mu fadi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil'adama da na nuna wariyar launin fata da suka gabata, za mu yi nasara, domin tare mun fi ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe wasu daga cikin masu fasahar da za su yi a taron na bana a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
