Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kirkirar sabuwar intanet domin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana kaddamar da sabuwar kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin karshe na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da Berners-Lee's open source dandamali Solid.
Tsarin dandamali na Solid yana bawa masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da za su iya samun damar wasu bayanai.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi barkwanci cewa niyyar ɓoye ta Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfani mai tasowa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandamali na Solid don bawa masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar nasu "ma'ajiyar bayanan kan layi na sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify. Dukansu suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan kan layi na sirri shine cewa mai amfani shine ke yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar wasu bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya hada da albarkatu, matakai da kuma iyawa don kowa ya sami damar amfani da dandalin Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu haka ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka samfuri da aka yi wa kwangila don aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta hanyar kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce babu wani daga cikin tawagarsa da ke magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko ya kamata a kawo sauyi mai zurfi inda duk tsarin kasuwanci ya zama babu komai cikin dare.
"Ba ma neman izinin su".
A cikin wani rubutu na Asabar a cikin Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa imashin Inrupt shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma yanayin muhalli don taimakawa kare mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizon da aka haɗa a cikin dandalin Solid.
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da lokacin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Open.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
