Tsohon kocin Alloa Athletic ya ce ba ya jin matsin lamba na zama na gaba a jerin sunayen da aka tsarkake a irin wannan babbar kungiya, bayan da ya ƙi ba da shawarwari daga Barnsley da Ipswich Town.
A yanzu, abin da zan yi amfani da shi wajen ganin na yi nasara shi ne, ko zan iya sa wannan tawagar ta koma gasar Premier.
Ya ce, "da yake ana ganin tsarin da kuma wuraren da kungiyar take ciki, a bayyane yake cewa matsayinta a gasar Premier League ne".
