Ross yana da shekaru uku ne kawai na kwarewa a matsayin kocin, bayan wani lokaci a matsayin kocin na biyu a Dumbarton da watanni 15 a cikin kwamitin Hearts.
Ya taimaka wa Alloa ta guji faduwa zuwa rukuni na uku kuma ya canza St Mirren daga gwagwarmayar ceto zuwa zakarun Championship a kakar wasa mai zuwa.
Ross ya ce yanzu ya fi jin dadi fiye da lokacin da yake a Clyde, Hartlepool, Falkirk, St Mirren da Hamilton Academical.
"Wataƙila lokaci ne mai mahimmanci", ya tuna game da karɓar mukamin a Alloa.
A koyaushe ina ganin cewa horarwa ne ya fi kyau fiye da wasa.
Abin mamaki ne, domin na yi kyau, na yi kyau, kuma na ji daɗin lokacin da na yi kyau.
Amma yin wasa zai iya zama da wuya.
