Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda hukumomi suka ce, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tun da an katse hanyoyin sadarwa, ba a samu damar samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu da ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Cèlebes ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuntar bay a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Cèlebes, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala yanki ne wanda ya kai tsawon kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Cèlebes.
A cikin shekara ta 2017, mazaunan yankin sun kai kimanin 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Célébes ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Harkokin nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an maida hankali ne, galibi, a Morowali, a gabar tekun a ƙarshen Cèlebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala da yawa tsunami a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar rage bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 kuma tsunami ya afku a yammacin Donggala wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Fire Belt kuma tana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
A nan an lissafa manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na shekarun baya:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Ace na Indonesiya, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani jerin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Dubban mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar tekun kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta girgiza wani yanki a garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke gaɓar tekun Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai saurin kaiwa Pidie Jaya Regency a Aceh ya haifar da lalacewa da fargaba, yayin da jama'a suka tuna da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ba a sami wata annobar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Lombok da ke Indonesia, inda mutane fiye da 500 suka mutu, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin yanayi na ɗan lokaci.
