Masu gabatar da kara na New York sun nemi a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addancin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas: hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a titin keke a kan titin keke na West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan kuma ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma masu hawan keke a kan hanyarsu a watan Oktoba.
