Dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce ya kamata a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a matsayin mai kula da tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "karfafa rundunar jama'a" a yau yayin zanga-zanga a taron jam'iyyar Conservative.
Tsohon shugaban UKIP ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba daga masu shakkar Turai" lokacin da wani dan majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ta jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya fada a taron Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta riga ta fice daga EU idan Mr Farage ne sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sasantawa tsakanin masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar da ke da rabuwa ya bayyana ne lokacin da masu goyon bayan jam'iyyar suka fito a wani zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewarsu da Brexit a birnin La City.
Firayim Minista na fafutukar kiyaye shirin ta na Chequers a tsakanin hare-haren masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu goyon bayan Tarayyar Turai da EU.
Abokan hulda sun nace cewa zai cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da martani mara kyau kuma suna matsawa masu shakkar Turai da jam'iyyar Conservative su zabi tsakanin kunshin su da rudani.
Mista Bone ya fadawa taron Leave Means Leave na Solihull cewa yana son ya soke alkawarin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a nada Mr Farage a matsayin dan majalisar dokoki kuma ya kamata a ba shi alhakin tattaunawar da Brussels.
'Idan ya kasance a cikin iko, za mu kasance a waje,' in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan kare Brexit, amma dole ne mu cire alkawarin Chequers".
Don bayyana adawarsa ga EU, ya kara da cewa: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama bayi ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da shawarwarin da ke cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun daga zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa jama'ar Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son zama a ciki ba gaskiya bane".
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ta halarci wannan gangamin kuma ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina gaya muku ne, Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane".
"Shawara ta Chequers ba ta da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da ita ba, ba ta da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutuka, waɗanda su ne mutanen da suka fita kan titi kuma suka sa mu lashe zabe.
