Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun gyara rashin nasarar da suka sha a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite da Belfast Giants, yayin da suka ci wasan sake bugawa 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Nan da nan, Giants sun sami nasara da kwallaye biyu ta hanyar wasan da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka yi.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun karawa tawagarsu girma, amma daga baya Dwyer ya dawo da Giants a gaba.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita Dundee, sannan Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka sha kaye a gasar Elite League, bayan sun ci Dundee 2-1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka yi a kakar wasa, kuma Giants sun lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Wasan farko ya zo ne daga hannun Dwyer a minti na huɗu, a 3:35, daga taimakon Kendall McFaull. Bayan minti huɗu, tare da taimakon David Rutherford, Beauvillier zai ninka ragamarsa.
A wannan lokacin tashin hankali, Sullivan ya sake sanya ƙungiyar gida a cikin wasan a minti na 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba da damar daidaitawa a minti na 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da Giants a farkon hutu lokacin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu na dare a ƙarshen farkon.
Kungiyar ta gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma, Bouchard ya sake ba da gudummawa ga matakin su tare da babbar nasara a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar farko a wasan a ƙarshen rabin kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagarsa tare da ci na biyar a ƙarshen wasan.
Giants, da suka yi rashin wasa hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka gabata, suna gida a Milton Keynes kuma suna da wasansu na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da jirgin sama ya mutu don ceton daruruwan fasinjojin jirgin sama daga girgizar kasa
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia ya zama jarumi bayan ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama mai dauke da daruruwan fasinjoji ya sauka lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma da yawa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Celebes ranar Juma'a kuma ta haifar da tsunami.
An samu girgizar kasa da dama a yankin kuma mutane da dama sun makale a cikin ramin da ke birnin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun tsere domin su ceci rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, mai shekara 21, ya ki barin wurinsa a hasumiyar kula da filin jirgin saman Palu Mutiara Sis Al Jufri.
Ya tsaya a wurin don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik 6321, wanda ke kan hanyar jirgin a lokacin, zai iya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya fita daga hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama lokacin da ya yi tunanin zai rushe.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Wakilin kamfanin Air Navigation, Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, kamar yadda ABC News ta Australia ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya wani jirgi mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan zuwa Kalimantan don kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
"Wannan ya karya mana zuciya", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu na iya kaiwa dubbai, yayin da hukumar rage yawan bala'i ta sanar da cewa an takaita samun damar zuwa garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu saboda har yanzu akwai gawawwaki da yawa a karkashin ramin kuma har yanzu akwai wadanda ba a iya samunsu ba", in ji wakilin hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Ruwa mai tsawon mita shida ya lalata Palu, wanda zai yi jana'izar kowa a ranar Lahadi.
Sojoji da wasu jiragen kasuwanci suna kawo kayan agaji da kayan abinci.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiyar 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowane minti, ana kawo gawawwakin mutane a motar asibiti.
Ruwa mai tsafta yana da ƙaranci.
An sace dukan kayayyakin da aka sayar a kasuwa".
Jan Gelfand, darektan Hukumar Ceton Ja-Gora ta Duniya a Indonesia, ya bayyana wa CNN cewa: "Ceton Ja-Gora na Indonesia na aiki tukuru don taimaka wa waɗanda suka tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya ƙara muni".
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin: "Ina rokon ku duka ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala dukkan ayyukan da suka shafi kwashe mutane.
Shin kun shirya?" In ji CNN.
Indonesia ta sha wahala daga wani girgizar kasa a wannan shekarar a Lombok, inda mutane sama da 550 suka mutu.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Air Niugini ta ce yanzu an rasa mutum daya bayan hatsarin tafkin
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ke aiki da jirgin da zai yi hatsari a wani tafkin tekun Pacific a Micronesia yanzu ya ce mutum ɗaya ya bace, duk da cewa a baya sun ce fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun kwashe jirgin da ke nitsewa lafiya.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa, tun da yammacin Asabar, ba su sami wani fasinja ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin gari, asibitoci da masu bincike don kokarin gano shi.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa ba da sauri ga buƙatun ƙarin cikakkun bayanai game da fasinja, kamar shekarunsa ko asalinsa.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceto wasu fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin lokacin da jirgin ya fada cikin ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman tsibirin Chuuk.
Hukumomi sun sanar a ranar Juma'a cewa an kwashe mutane bakwai zuwa asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce a ranar Asabar, akwai fasinjoji shida a asibiti kuma dukansu suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san dalilin hatsarin da kuma ainihin abubuwan da suka faru ba.
Kamfanin jiragen sama da na Amurka sun ce jirgin ya rataya a tafkin ne saboda hanyarsa ta yi kasa.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya ratsa hanyar jirgin.
Wani fasinja dan Amurka mai suna Bill Jaynes ya bayyana cewa jirgin yana sauka sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu fasinjoji sun yi tafiya a cikin ruwa a cikin belin su zuwa hanyar fita daga jirgin, wanda ke nitsewa.
