Sojojin ruwan Amurka sun ce masu aikin ruwa da ke aiki kusa da wurin don inganta wani tashar jirgin ruwa sun kuma taimaka wajen ceto tare da jirgin ruwa mai kumfa don kai mutanen da abin ya shafa zuwa gabar teku kafin jirgin ya nutse mita 30 a cikin ruwa.
Bayanai daga Cibiyar Tsaron Jiragen Sama sun nuna cewa mutane 111 sun mutu a hatsarin jiragen sama da aka yi rajista a PNG, amma Air Niugini ba ta da hannu a cikin waɗannan haɗarin.
Wani mai sharhi ya rubuta tarihin daren da aka kona wata mace
Masu gabatar da kara sun kammala shari'ar ne a ranar Asabar a lokacin da suke sake duba shari'ar wani mutum da ake zargi da kona wata mata a Mississippi a shekarar 2014.
Mai bincike na Ma'aikatar Shari'a Paul Rowlett ya yi shaida na sa'o'i da yawa a matsayin gwani a fannin nazarin bayanan sirri.
Ya bayyana wa alƙalan yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan wayar salula don gina motsin mai laifi, Quinton Tellis, mai shekara 29, da kuma wanda aka kashe, Jessica Chambers, mai shekara 19, a daren da aka kashe shi.
Rowlett ta ce ta sami bayanan wurin da aka samu daga wayoyin salula daban-daban da ke nuna cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren da ta mutu, wanda ya sabawa bayanan da ta yi a baya, kamar yadda The Clarion Ledger ta ruwaito.
Lokacin da bayanan suka nuna cewa wayar salula tana tare da Chambers a lokacin da ya yi ikirarin cewa yana tare da abokinsa Michael Sanford, 'yan sanda sun je sun yi magana da Sanford.
A ranar Asabar, Sanford ya musanta hakan kuma ya shaida cewa ba ya cikin gari a ranar.
"Sa'ad da aka tambayi masu gabatar da kara ko Tellis ya faɗi gaskiya sa'ad da ya ce yana cikin motar Sanford a wannan daren, Sanford ya ce ya yi ƙarya, tun da motarsa tana Nashville".
Wani rashin daidaito shine Tellis ya bayyana cewa ya kasance yana da makonni biyu da sanin Chambers lokacin da ya mutu.
An rubuta cewa sun san juna ne tun mako guda da suka wuce.
Rowlett ta ce, wani lokaci bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya goge saƙonnin rubutu, kira, da bayanin tuntuɓar Chambers daga wayar sa.
"Ya shafe ta daga rayuwarsa", in ji Hale.
Masu kare sun shirya fara jawabin su na karshe a ranar Lahadi.
