The High Breed: Menene hip-hop mai hankali?
Wani rukunin mawaƙa na hip-hop ya cika waƙoƙin sa da saƙo mai kyau don ƙalubalanci ra'ayi mara kyau game da jinsi.
The High Breed, daga Bristol, ya tabbatar da cewa hip-hop ya rabu da asalinsa tare da saƙonnin siyasa da matsalolin zamantakewa.
Suna son komawa ga asalinsu kuma su sake sanya hip-hop mai hankali.
Wasu masu fasaha, kamar su The Fugees da Common, sun sami farfadowa a cikin kwanan nan a Burtaniya ta hannun masu fasaha kamar Akala da Lowkey.
Wani baƙar fata?!
Wata 'yar'uwa mai zaman kanta a birnin New York ta bukaci a sallami wasu ma'aurata bayan an rubuta musu saƙon nuna wariyar launin fata.
Wata 'yar makaranta a birnin New York ta kai karar saurin kore ma'aurata bayan da mahaifiyarta ta aika mata da sakon rubutu da ba daidai ba, tana nuna rashin amincewa da ita domin ita "wata bakar fata ce".
Ma'auratan sun musanta cewa su masu wariyar launin fata ne kuma suna kwatanta karar da "cin hanci da rashawa".
Lynsey Plasco-Flaxman, mahaifiyar yara biyu, ta nuna takaicinta da ganin cewa sabuwar mai kula da yara, Giselle Maurice, baƙar fata ce lokacin da ta fara aiki a ranar farko a shekara ta 2016.
"NOOOOOOOOOOOO DAYA DAYA NA bakar fata", in ji Mrs Plasco-Flaxman ga mijinta a cikin saƙon rubutu.
Amma maimakon ta aika da shi ga mijinta, ta aika da shi ga Madame Maurice, sau biyu.
Bayan ta gano cewa tana da rashin hankali, wata "mai ban haushi" Mrs. Plasco-Flaxman ta sallami Mrs. Maurice, duk da cewa mai kula da ita da ta sallame, wacce baƙar fata ce, ta yi aikinta ba daidai ba kuma tana jiran wani ɗan Filipin, a cewar New York Post.
An biya Malama Maurice albashi na ranar aiki, sannan aka tura ta gida a cikin motar Uber.
